#README

---> generates 
	-) neutrons w/ energy according to spectrum found in file (data/*.dat), neutron position randomly distributed in stainless steel tank
        -) neutrons or other particles with a flat random energy distribution

Usage: ardm_mc N(particles) particleType(e.g. 'e-')
choose starting volume for neutrons and file(e.g. 'SS_238U') + reaction_type('an' or 'sf') later, if desired
